divisibility antichains cover all sufficiently large integers. The key difficulty is
upgrading interval-style coverage (Frobenius/coin problem) to antichain-sum coverage.
-/
theorem erdos_123_d_complete_sequences :
    ∀ a b c : ℕ, 1 < a → 1 < b → 1 < c →
      PairwiseCoprime3 a b c →
      IsDComplete (PowTripleSet a b c) := by
  sorry

